{"id": "1453432431536377907", "channel_id": "1453430808919543879", "type": 0, "author_id": "599171149431046156", "author_name": "foxcatfurry", "author_bot": false, "content": "幫忙問(", "timestamp": "2025-12-24T17:01:35.147000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1453430808919543879", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "对于联动的期限规划 On the Duration and Planning of Collaborations", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1453432460934119465", "channel_id": "1453430808919543879", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "Our view and planning for collaborations are quite different from most games.\n\nOur focus is not on short-term commercial monetization, but on exploring more possibilities for collaborative works within Morimens. Given that our production capacity has always been limited and precious, we’ve further decided that all collaboration content we create will be designed as long-term, permanent additions to the game. This is the basic premise under which we approach any collab.\n\nOf course, specific titles may still have different licensing terms depending on the situation. In general, the license period will be at least several years, with no limit on the number of uses worldwide. As a result, the rules for obtaining collaboration characters and their rerun plans will, in most cases, be similar to other limited Awakeners in the game. The associated story content will also remain permanently available.\n\nTaking Mist Sequence as an example, the license period is permanent, and we may also release merch for Mouchette from Morimens in the future. For other works with a fixed license term, we will make an announcement before the content is taken down once the term expires.\nWe’ve noticed that many players are concerned about how long collaboration content will remain in the game, so we hope this dev log can clear up some of those questions.\n\nAside from Mist Sequence, we are also in talks to collaborate with other titles—including some single-player games that have had a profound influence on members of the B.I.A.V.Studio . I honestly can’t wait to share more detailed information with you once everything is more firmly decided!", "timestamp": "2025-12-24T17:01:42.156000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-24T17:10:40.365000+00:00", "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 73}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1453430808919543879", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "对于联动的期限规划 On the Duration and Planning of Collaborations", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
